    <title>libxslt (For XSLT transformation)</title>
    <para>
        This is a set of low-level, cross-platform utilities to transform xml using XSLT style sheets.
        Originally part of the <emphasis>Gnome</emphasis> desktop project, <literal>libxml</literal>
        can be downloaded from <ulink url="http://xmlsoft.org/XSLT/"/>.
    </para>
